metadata.description:
Bahdoon welcomes you to the Gold Lion Club

ALL the information regarding the details of the sub are displayed dynamically and in real time
on your token image. All info is LIVE

Gold Lion Club is our 26 week ~ 6 Month Subscription plan

The hodler of this token will be able to mint

-26 RedLion Gazette issues
-26 ArtDrops
-Discord Gold Lion Role
-Sub Rewards (if any that period)

The subscription starts from the following week of the mint.
I.e. If you mint while issue 50 is live your subscription will start on issue 51.

The hodler has 8 weeks ~ 2 months time to mint the corresponding Gazettes from the time of their issuance, respectively.

Then the issue owners have a total of 8 weeks ~ 2 months to claim their ArtDrop.

After the 2 month period unclaimed Gazettes will be lost forever and the final supply is locked.

This subscription is tradeable, however after it's expired the image will display EXPIRED
If you buy on secondary make sure you understand how many issues are left and how much you are paying

Visit redlion.news and connect your wallet to view extra information enter Subscriber Secret Base and also view your Gazette Collection

All sales are final.
Please trade carefully.

Make sure you are aware of all the data and read carefully all the info before you buy.
Due to the nature of blockchain transactions we cannot revert user errors.

We are excited to have you onboard
LFG
